snippet.title: CTGP-7 - Trailer
snippet.description:
CTGP-7 is a modpack for Mario Kart 7 which includes many new features to the game, including community made custom tracks and characters, as well as new game modes and settings!

You can read more about CTGP-7 here: https://gbatemp.net/threads/mario-kart-7-custom-track-grand-prix-7-ctgp-7.396936/

Music by Manel Navola: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1eIv2KitI_w
Footage recorded by fishguy6564: https://www.youtube.com/user/fishguy6564

This trailer has been showcased in Kaze Emanuar's F3 2020 presentation: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i_MlRkciRaY

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discord Server: https://discordapp.com/invite/0uTPwYv3SPQww54l
